# 🏥 AI Pharmacy OS — Comprehensive Audit & Implementation Plan

## Executive Summary

This is a **deep, line-by-line audit** of the entire AI Pharmacy project. The system is a Node.js/TypeScript Express server that powers a 19-page pharmacy management OS. The backend has good bones, but there are **critical bugs, incomplete wiring, missing DB columns, duplicate exports, and broken UI↔API contracts** throughout. This plan catalogs every issue and provides exact fixes.

---

## 🔴 CRITICAL BUGS (Must Fix First — These Break Core Functions)

### BUG-01: `emailService.ts` — Duplicate Export (Server Won't Start)
**File:** [`emailService.ts`](file:///E:/CURRENT%20PROJECT%20ON%20WORKING/AI%20PHARMACY/src/services/emailService.ts#L486-L492)  
**Error:** Lines 486–492 have `export const emailService` and `export default emailService` duplicated twice. This is a **syntax error** that will crash the TypeScript compiler.
```diff
- // Export singleton instance (lines 490-492 are duplicates)
- export const emailService = new EmailService();
- export default emailService;
```
**Fix:** Delete lines 490–492 (the second duplicate block).

